Latency Components Stacked Bar Chart: T_network (50-200ms), T_queue (variable), T_prompt (scales with prompt length), T_generation (scales with output tokens), T_post (<10ms). Total bar per configuration. Annotations: "Network: Region choice matters", "Queue: Rate limiting effect", "Prompt: 10K tokens = 5-15x 1K", "Generation: Quadratic with context". German labels, data viz style.